            <p class="mt-2 text-[16px] font-normal text-[#000000] leading-[28px]">
                Launched on 27th September 2021, the Ayushman Bharat Digital Mission (ABDM) aims to enhance healthcare accessibility and equity through digital innovation. By leveraging IT, it supports existing health systems with a citizen-centric approach. ABDM envisions a unified digital health ecosystem that ensures efficient, inclusive, affordable, and secure healthcare for all. The mission improves efficiency, transparency, and accessibility, allowing individuals to choose between public and private services, while healthcare professionals gain better access to patient records for improved care.
