                The Healthcare Professionals Registry (HPR), a key initiative under ABDM, is a comprehensive digital repository of healthcare professionals across modern and traditional medicine in India. Enrolling in HPR enables professionals to seamlessly integrate into India’s digital health ecosystem, enhancing accessibility, efficiency, and care quality. This centralized directory ensures verified access to skilled professionals for patients and healthcare providers. HPR also improves interoperability, connecting professionals with health facilities, digital records, and government initiatives, fostering a transparent, patient-centric healthcare system.
